WEBVTT

00:00:00.817 --> 00:00:04.087
So I had this very interesting experience

00:00:04.111 --> 00:00:05.261
five years ago.

00:00:06.278 --> 00:00:09.103
You know, me and my husband,
we were out grocery shopping,

00:00:09.127 --> 00:00:10.720
as we do every other day,

00:00:10.744 --> 00:00:14.093
but this time, we found this fancy,

00:00:14.117 --> 00:00:17.839
you know, I'm talking fair-trade,
I'm talking organic,

00:00:17.863 --> 00:00:20.395
I'm talking Kenyan, single-origin coffee

00:00:20.419 --> 00:00:22.152
that we splurged and got.

00:00:23.252 --> 00:00:26.554
And that was when the problem
started already.

00:00:26.578 --> 00:00:30.418
You know, my husband,
he deemed this coffee blend superior